  "desc": {
    "en": "Place the glowing object below the character, firing upward. Reverse the direction of the light and shadows land where they normally never do.",
    "zh": "把發光物體放到角色下方往上打，光的方向一反轉，陰影就會落在平常不會出現的位置。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "Our eyes expect light from above, so light from below instinctively feels unsettling. It is a staple of horror films.",
    "zh": "人眼習慣光來自上方，由下往上的光會本能地讓人覺得不安，這是恐怖片常用的手法。"
  },
